author: Doreen Christensen
title: Free $150 health screenings at Sam's Club on Saturday
text:
Free $150 health screenings at Sam's Club on Saturday October is the last month free health screenings will be offered at Sam's Club in 2015. Get $150 in free health tests at Sam's Club on Saturday, Oct. 10. 
Get free $150 health screenings at Sam's Club pharmacy on Saturday. 
Stop in from 11 a.m. to 3 p.m., get free wellness checks on glucose, total cholesterol, HDL (good cholesterol), blood pressure and body fat percentage. 
The tests are performed by licensed technicians. Area pharmacies charge up to $60 for some of these tests. 
You do not need a Sam's Club membership to use the pharmacy or get the free screenings. 
This is the last month this year free tests will be offered by the warehouse chain.
